com.tigertext.ttandroid.user

Class UserManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tigertext.ttandroid.user.UserManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TTPubSub.Listener

    public class UserManager
extends java.lang.Object
implements TTPubSub.Listener
    Created by gautamkanwar on 9/24/15.

    This class holds all the stuff related to a user. This class should have user cache, persistence, http calls everything related to a user. Essentially it should be a local user repo.

      • getParticipantInCache

        @Nullable
public Participant getParticipantInCache(@NonNull
                                                   java.lang.String participantId,
                                                   @NonNull
                                                   java.lang.String orgId)
        Returns:
        The participant with the given id and org id, or null if none exists in the cache. This is the preferred method to get participants synchronously on the main thread, since DB transactions and network requests could block for an extended period of time. If the cache doesn't contain the participant, consider using getParticipantSync(String, String) on a worker thread to load this participant from the DB or network
